<h2 align="center" id="-installation">ğŸ“¦ Installation</h2>

### Prerequisites

> ğŸ Python 3.10 or higher with pip or uv package manager

### From PyPI (Recommended)

```bash
# Install from PyPI
pip install argus_uav

# Verify installation
argus --help
```

### From Source (For Development)

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/Sang-Buster/Argus.git
cd Argus

# Create virtual environment
uv sync
source venv/bin/activate  # On Windows: venv\Scripts\activate

# Verify installation
argus --help
pytest tests/ -v
```

